    {
      "id": "PopularPost350175",
      "post_content": "I do not understand how this could possibly be confusing. Serious face, here. I once got one in a card lot and read it and instantly understood. I don't see why anyone is bitching about the rules text because you just have to understand what the words mean.  \n  \nIt's the \"rules correct\" way of switching over a blocker. A lot of the clauses are so that you can't have a creature double chump block two different creatures as the first would still be blocked if there weren't the clauses. Tut tut.  \n  \n5/5",
      "posted_by": "MCcreator",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost350175\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">I do not understand how this could possibly be confusing. Serious face, here. I once got one in a card lot and read it and instantly understood. I don't see why anyone is bitching about the rules text because you just have to understand what the words mean.<br/><br/>It's the \"rules correct\" way of switching over a blocker. A lot of the clauses are so that you can't have a creature double chump block two different creatures as the first would still be blocked if there weren't the clauses. Tut tut.<br/><br/>5/5</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '350175'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy89116\">MCcreator</span>\r\n                                (11/6/2013 11:08:26 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../.